@startuml Virtual_Fridge
title Use Case Diagram: Virtual Fridge (UC5)

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white

left to right direction

actor "User" as User #4ECDC4

rectangle "Virtual Fridge System" {
  usecase "UCS05-1\nAdd Ingredient" as UC1 #E0F0FF
  usecase "UCS05-2\nView Ingredient List" as UC2 #E0F0FF
  usecase "UCS05-3\nUpdate Ingredient" as UC3 #E0F0FF
  usecase "UCS05-4\nRemove Ingredient" as UC4 #E0F0FF
}

User --> UC1
User --> UC2
User --> UC3
User --> UC4

' Relationships
UC3 ..> UC2 : <<include>>
UC4 ..> UC2 : <<include>>

note right of UC1
  Add with quantity, unit, expiry
  Autocomplete from standardized DB
  Barcode scanner
  Batch CSV import
  Merge duplicates
end note

note right of UC2
  View all ingredients
  Color-coded warnings:
  - Expired (red)
  - Expiring soon (yellow)
  Filter by status/category
  Sort by name/expiry date
  Paginate 50 items
end note

note right of UC3
  Update quantity/unit/expiry
  Quick +/- buttons
  Auto unit conversion
  (1000g = 1kg)
  Batch update
end note

note right of UC4
  Remove ingredient
  Confirmation dialog
  Suggest move to shopping list
  Batch delete
  Auto-delete expired (optional)
end note

note bottom of UC2
  Smart Inventory Management:
  - Expiry tracking
  - Unit conversion
  - Shopping list integration
end note

@enduml




